name: ALTON Vouchers Pre-Market
description:
ALTON vouchers give you the opportunity to purchase our tokens at the lowest price before they hit the market.

After TGE, the vouchers will automatically be exchanged for tokens through a secure smart contract.

The number of tokens is limited by a unique smart contract, making them a valuable asset.

By purchasing a voucher now, you become part of the future of DeFi on the TON blockchain. Don't miss your chance to invest in a promising project!
